snippet: Officials, brokers and developers are debating whether resurgent commercial and residential real estate markets are a cause for jubilation or concern.
abstract: Officials, brokers and developers are debating whether Indonesia's resurgent commercial and residential real estate markets are a cause for jubilation or concern; high rents and prices have been subject of particular scrutiny because real estate helped cause financial collapse in late 1990s and because currency has been one of hardest hit among emerging markets in recent months.
lead_paragraph: Officials, brokers and developers are debating whether resurgent commercial and residential real estate markets are a cause for jubilation or concern.

headline.main: Real Estate Heating Up in Indonesia
headline.print_headline: Real Estate Heating Up In Indonesia
